        <title>Ardal, Dieu du Sanzu - Illustration à l&#x27;encre</title>
        <author>
            <name>Lonan Aedhia</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/ardal-dieu-du-sanzu-illustration-a-lencre.html"/>
        <id>https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/ardal-dieu-du-sanzu-illustration-a-lencre.html</id>
            <category term="Miroir des Âmes"/>

        <updated>2022-05-20T17:07:09+02:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                        <img src="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/Ardal-01.jpg" alt="Ardal Sanzu Illustration encre papier" />
                    Ardal s'éveille après un comas de douze ans au fond du fleuve&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <img src="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/Ardal-01.jpg" alt="Ardal Sanzu Illustration encre papier" />
                <figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/Ardal-01.Ban1.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01.Ban1-xs.jpg 300w ,https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01.Ban1-sm.jpg 480w ,https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01.Ban1-md.jpg 768w ,https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01.Ban1-lg.jpg 1024w"  alt="" width="1800" height="606"></figure>
<p>Ardal s'éveille après un comas de douze ans au fond du fleuve magique, le Sanzu. Ce fleuve invoqué par sa compagne, Lifh, pour le sauver des flammes dieu fou Déméthos devient le principal obstacle entre elle et Ardal pour se retrouver.  Au terme d'une quête, Ardal devient le dieu du Sanzu… Mais tout dieu qu'il est, pourra-t-il retrouver Lifh ? </p>
<figure class="post__image post__image--wide"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/Ardal-01-2.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01-2-xs.jpg 300w ,https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01-2-sm.jpg 480w ,https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01-2-md.jpg 768w ,https://lonanaedhia.github.io/Illustration/media/posts/3/responsive/Ardal-01-2-lg.jpg 1024w"  alt="Illustration encre, Ardal dieu du Sanzu, par Lonan Aedhia" width="733" height="1000"></figure>
            ]]>
        </content>
